<div class="container my-5">
  <h1 class="text-maroon border-bottom pb-2 mb-4">Audition Information</h1>
  
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <p class="lead">Join the Voice of Aggieland. Auditions for the Singing Cadets are held at the beginning of the Fall and Spring semesters.</p>

      <ul class="nav nav-tabs mt-5" id="auditionTabs" role="tablist">
        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
          <button class="nav-link active" id="upcoming-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#upcoming" type="button" role="tab">
            Current & Upcoming Auditions
          </button>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
          <button class="nav-link" id="past-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#past" type="button" role="tab">
            Past Auditions
          </button>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="tab-content mt-3" id="auditionTabContent">
        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="upcoming" role="tabpanel">
          <% if @current_auditions.any? || @future_auditions.any? %>
            <% @current_auditions.each do |session| %>
              <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3"><%= session.label %></h3>
              <div class="card border-0 mb-4 border-start border-maroon border-4" style="box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 128, 0, 0.4) !important;">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                    <li class="mb-2">
                      <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>Start:</strong> <%= session.start_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>End:</strong> <%= session.end_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-2">
                      <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>Location:</strong> <%= session.location %>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
            <% @future_auditions.each do |session| %>
              <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3"><%= session.label %></h3>
              <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4 border-start border-maroon border-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                    <li class="mb-2">
                      <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>Start:</strong> <%= session.start_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>End:</strong> <%= session.end_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-2">
                      <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>Location:</strong> <%= session.location %>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          <% else %>
            <p class="text-muted mt-4">Audition dates have not been announced yet. Check back soon!</p>
          <% end %>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="past" role="tabpanel">
          <% if @past_auditions.any? %>
            <% @past_auditions.each do |session| %>
              <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3"><%= session.label %></h3>
              <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4 border-start border-maroon border-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                    <li class="mb-2">
                      <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>Start:</strong> <%= session.start_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>End:</strong> <%= session.end_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-2">
                      <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <strong>Location:</strong> <%= session.location %>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          <% else %>
            <p class="text-muted mt-4">No past auditions on record.</p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3">What to Expect</h3>
      <p>The audition process is straightforward. No prepared piece is necessary. The director will guide you through simple vocal exercises to determine your range and pitch matching ability.</p>
      
      <div class="alert bg-light border mt-4">
        <h5 class="alert-heading"><i class="bi bi-question-circle me-2" aria-hidden="true"></i> Do I need to be a music major?</h5>
        <p class="mb-0">No! The Singing Cadets represent almost every major at Texas A&M. A passion for music and dedication to the group are what matter most.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>